parameters: \n<Girl>"I won't forgive you. That knight... how dare...!"

\n<Girl>"I'll kill him! I'll kill him with my own hands!
Definitely!"
\n<???>"I am everywhere. Anywhere there's a delicious smell."

\n<???>"I've been watching you all this time. You've had it
tough... with your mother being killed."

\n<???>"It's painful, isn't it? You hate them, don't you? You want
to get back at them, right?"

\n<???>"I want to be your strength. If you'd like, let me help you
with that."

\n<???>"All you have to do is entrust yourself to me. Then, I'll
help make your wish come true."

\n<???>"I want to hear it from your lips. What you want the most
right now. What you desire the most right now."
\n<Girl>"I want to kill the knight who killed my mother..."

\n<Girl>"I am a succubus! If he killed my mother as a knight, then
as a succubus, I will corrupt him!"

\n<Girl>"And once he's corrupted, I'll make him apologize! Right
here! To my mother, for succumbing to pleasure!"

\n<Girl>"I want to corrupt him! I want to seduce him into depravity!
I'll engulf both his body and mind in pleasure!"

\n<Begieade>"Of course. I shall lend you the power to fulfill your
wish."
\n<Begieade>"...If you'll listen to a little request of mine."
\n<Begieade>"From now on, you will become my Lyric."
